data.description: This wonderful home is on the South end of Ozark in between Ozark and Branson.  This is a very well kept all brick custom built home that sits on 5 acres.  3 bedrooms, 3 1/2 baths, walkout basement, formal dining room, large kitchen, breakfast bar, and a 3rd bay garage in the basement.  Do you need another bedroom? No problem,,,There is room in the basement to finish one.  Relax on your beautiful covered deck or patio and enjoy the amazing views the Ozarks has to offer.  Don't miss out on this beauty!!  The Seller is providing a home warranty.
